text: Tboung Khmum is a province in Cambodia. The capital city is Suong. There are 6 districts and 1 municipality: *Dambae *Krouch Chhmar *Memot *Ou Reang Ov *Ponhea Kraek *Suong Municipality *Tboung Khmum ==References== Category:Provinces of Cambodia Category:Establishments in Cambodia Category:2013 establishments in Asia
